{"tid":1981133,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"真攬炒系列19: 本港最新失業率4.2%　超過9年來高位","createTime":"2020-04-20T13:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-21T10:53:53.000Z","uid":292292,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"86f6e2e6e5b3636462fb46915e906c98c67d9571","tid":1981133,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:12:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521642-20200420.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521642-20200420.htm&d=1E6MrqGGcFSEGQF%2FdL0KzZE%2BEEUKUWA%2FtqiTfwOa%2F%2FE%3D&h=06d537a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1521642-20200420.htm&h=f83b58a4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1521642-20200420.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n政府公布，本年1月至3月的失業率為4.2%，較去年12月至今年2月的數字上升0.5個百分點，為超過9年來的高位。就業不足率亦升0.6個百分點至2.1%，為接近10年來的高位。<br />\n<br />\n大多數主要經濟行業的失業率及就業不足率都上升，升幅較為顯著的包括建造業、教育業、運輸業和零售、住宿及膳食服務業。<br />\n<br />\n勞工及福利局局長羅致光表示，與消費及旅遊相關行業合計失業率升至6.8%，為2009年全球金融危機爆發後的最高水平，就業不足率則升至3.9%，為自2003年受沙士打擊後的高位。<br />\n<br />\n羅致光說，勞工市場在短期內，將繼續面對疫情對經濟衝擊所帶來的巨大壓力，為確保經濟活力及減輕市民的財政負擔，政府已推出歷來最大規模的紓緩措施。"},{"pid":"75d5e5033bc13bee6cad108624f31b43582e4bbc","tid":1981133,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:12:44.000Z","msg":"3,4月個數字應該去到6%"},{"pid":"3a2411afebe05a3bb321ca948735f6cc833d1253","tid":1981133,"uid":189638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:14:13.000Z","msg":"如果歐美真係要圍倒支那，之後個失業率會仲高。"},{"pid":"17ff2f50409231e6eb2f94973c5542f71c061966","tid":1981133,"uid":292292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75d5e5033bc13bee6cad108624f31b43582e4bbc","tid":1981133,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:12:44.000Z","msg":"3,4月個數字應該去到6%"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:20:34.000Z","msg":"4月應去到4尾<br />\n5月去到5頭"},{"pid":"3f338c1005230604dc151f7e9812e12030372ee6","tid":1981133,"uid":171866,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:43:35.000Z","msg":"6%都低<br />\n無薪假"},{"pid":"5b3a68bc66467f7654b718976b2930c92f63161c","tid":1981133,"uid":83582,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"75d5e5033bc13bee6cad108624f31b43582e4bbc","tid":1981133,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:12:44.000Z","msg":"3,4月個數字應該去到6%"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-20T13:45:04.000Z","msg":"未必再大升, 炒人冇資助"},{"pid":"0e4c3b71d7a9c7c986168ef77ffc2c75d373c728","tid":1981133,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:37:39.000Z","msg":"放心，政府繼續實施限制人群措施，失業率會長升長有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"edb04671a9771d9066c11b3fa384cd9bcddd5c5a","tid":1981133,"uid":56644,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:40:07.000Z","msg":"樓市繼續gồ gồ"},{"pid":"72bfa90970d88503a6f0ad9a502351ca63dbde4d","tid":1981133,"uid":10509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:47:09.000Z","msg":"好多人 no pay leave 唔計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84acb11f5786fbd21df9122c1493e59b0405a10c","tid":1981133,"uid":160193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-21T10:53:53.000Z","msg":"攬炒香港  失業革命<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}